&lt;/header>&lt;div class="row">
&lt;div class="col-sm col-md-6 mb-4">
&lt;div class="h-100 card shadow" href="#">
&lt;div class="card-body">
&lt;h4 class="card-title">
&lt;a href='https://dubbo.apache.org/zh-cn/overview/mannual/java-sdk/tasks/mesh/migration/dubbo-mesh/'>Istio &amp; Envoy 示例&lt;/a>
&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>演示 Dubbo 服务接入基于 Envoy 代理的 Istio 服务网格体系。&lt;/p>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="col-sm col-md-6 mb-4">
&lt;div class="h-100 card shadow">
&lt;div class="card-body">
&lt;h4 class="card-title">
&lt;a href='https://dubbo.apache.org/zh-cn/overview/mannual/java-sdk/tasks/mesh/migration/proxyless/'>Istio &amp; Proxyless 示例&lt;/a>
